# React Hooks Services Types

Use dedicated folders for reusable logic:

- `src/hooks/use<FeatureName>.ts` for reusable business logic
- `src/services/<featureName>Service.ts` for API calls only
- `src/types/<featureName>.types.ts` for shared types/interfaces
- `src/utils/<featureName>.ts` for pure helpers

Rules:

- Keep UI components presentation-first
- Avoid direct API calls in pages/components
- Type function inputs and outputs explicitly
- Avoid unnecessary `any`
